{"article_id":"sBZX9ldQXmTSKEhx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump canceled an invitation to the White House for the Super Bowl-winning Philadelphia Eagles on Monday ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that \" staying in the locker room for the playing of our National Anthem \" was \" disrespectful . \"","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"This explanation , however , makes no sense .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"No Eagles players ever stayed in the locker room during the national anthem ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"nor did any players kneel during the regular season or the playoffs .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"And","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"when Fox News tried to pile on","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"by showing footage of players","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"it claimed","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"were protesting during the national anthem ,","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"it backfired","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"- because those players weren ' t protesting ;","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"they were praying .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Trump believes","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that NFL anthem protests are a winning issue for him ;","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"after all , culture war politics have served him well .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The more the focus is on race and other identity issues ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"the better off he is .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"But conservatives are starting to reconsider their positions .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"On Tuesday evening , President Trump tweeted","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that he had canceled a planned visit by the Eagles to the White House","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"because only a small number of players intended to come ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that \" staying in the locker room \" for the national anthem was \" disrespectful . \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"The Philadelphia Eagles Football Team was invited to the White House .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Unfortunately , only a small number of players decided to come ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"and we canceled the event .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Staying in the Locker Room for the playing of our National Anthem is as disrespectful to our country as kneeling .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Sorry !","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"June 5 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Originally , the names of 70 players were submitted to the White House for the event ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"but Eagles players were still deciding on whether to go","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"( defensive end Chris Long would not attend ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"but quarterback Carson Wentz was planning to ) .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"After reportedly attempting to reschedule for when Trump would be in Singapore ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"the group","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that planned to be in attendance as of Monday morning","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"would have included a few players and the team ' s owner , Jeffrey Lurie .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"In 2017 , Patriots quarterback Tom Brady and more than two dozen other Patriots players skipped their White House visit","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"which went on as scheduled .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"In a statement , Trump said ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"\" The Philadelphia Eagles are unable to come to the White House with their full team","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"to be celebrated tomorrow .","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"They disagree with their President","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"because he insists","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"that they proudly stand for the National Anthem , hand on heart , in honor of the great men and women of our military and the people of our country .","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"The Eagles wanted to send a smaller delegation ,","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"but the 1,000 fans","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"planning to attend the event","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"deserve better . \"","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"Trump ' s statement wasn ' t true .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"No Eagles players kneeled during the season ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"nor did any stay in the locker room .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"If someone took a knee during those 16 games","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"I missed it","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"https : //t.co/hzMz9VKQC","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"2 - Torrey Smith","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"( @ TorreySmithWR )","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"June 5 , 2018","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Today ' s White House visit has been rebranded as a celebration of America","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"hosted by a president","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"who described the United States as a \" hellhole \" in May 2015 .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"We will proudly be playing the National Anthem and other wonderful music","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"celebrating our Country today at 3 P.M. , The White House , with the United States Marine Band and the United States Army Chorus .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Honoring America !","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"NFL , no escaping to Locker Rooms !","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"June 5 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"The controversy got worse","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"when Fox News picked up the story .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"In a television segment on the White House visit cancellation , Fox News used B-roll footage of Eagles players","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"kneeling before the anthem","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"- but didn ' t mention","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that the players","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"featured","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"were praying .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"Many Eagles players are Christians ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"and a group of players pray together before every game .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"In response , Zach Ertz , a tight end for the Eagles , tweeted","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"that Fox News should be \" better than this. \"","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Ertz is among the players","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"featured","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"praying in the Fox News segment -","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"he ' s a devout Christian ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and he and his teammates released a Bible study phone app on humility and surrender this past fall .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"This can ' t be serious ....","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Praying before games with my teammates , well before the anthem , is being used for your propaganda ? !","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"Just sad ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"I feel like","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"you guys should have to be better than this ...","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"https : //t.co/kYeyH2zXdK","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"- Zach Ertz","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"( @ ZERTZ_86 )","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"June 5 , 2018","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"Fox News eventually apologized ,","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"acknowledging in a statement to USA Today","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"that no Eagles players ever kneeled in protest during the season in 2017 :","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Update :","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"In a statement","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"provided to @ usatodaysports ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Fox News apologizes","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"for using footage of Eagles players","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"praying in its segment .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"pic.twitter.com/mGyir1f5dU","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"- Tom Schad","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"( @ Tom_Schad )","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"June 5 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Reportedly , Trump told Dallas Cowboys owner Jerry Jones","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"that the national anthem protests were \" a very winning , strong issue for [ him ] , \"","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"and the NFL has repeatedly tried to sate the president ' s anger on the subject ,","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"including banning players from kneeling in protest during the anthem at all earlier this spring .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"But the brouhaha over the Eagles ' White House visit appears to have backfired on Trump , including among conservative commentators and GOP members of Congress .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"Pennsylvania GOP Rep. Ryan Costello tweeted","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"that Trump handled the situation \" poorly \" :","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"Eagles my fave team .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Super Bowl win so meaningful as Philly sports fan .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"POTUS handled poorly .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"This is a depressing commentary on our political culture ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"very deflating to me .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"Was really excited for today .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"As a fan","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"who bleeds green .","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"Not going to WH .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"Disappointed in all of this .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"https : //t.co/YfgBQjzFgB","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"- Ryan Costello","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"( @ RyanCostello )","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"June 5 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Conservative magazine columnist Jonah Goldberg called Trump ' s statements \" deceitful propaganda \" :","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"The attempt","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"to make the Eagles event cancellation about the national anthem","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"is just a complete act of deceitful propaganda","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"and conservatives should have zero to do with it .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"If that was the issue ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"why schedule the event in the first place ?","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"Also :","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"None of them kneeled .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"Shameful .","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"- Jonah Goldberg","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"( @ JonahNRO )","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"June 5 , 2018","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"And RedState contributor Jim Jamitis pointed out the bad optics","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"of excitedly planning a meeting with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"while denigrating NFL players :","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"Our president is enthusiastically planning a meeting with a guy","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"who fed his uncle to starving dogs","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"but cancels a photo op","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"because football players hurt his feelings .","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"- Jim `` Jim '' Jamitis","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"( @ anthropocon )","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"June 5 , 2018","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"Trump may have thought","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"that his favorite pet peeve","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"- national anthem protests in the NFL -","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"would continue to win him support .","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"This time , he may have thought wrong .","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"In an email , a White House spokesperson asked","depth":3},{"id":162,"text":"that I include their updated statement in this article .","depth":3},{"id":163,"text":"In the statement , the White House alleges","depth":3},{"id":164,"text":"that the Philadelphia Eagles \" decided to abandon their fans \"","depth":4},{"id":165,"text":"by not attending the White House celebration .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":331,"left":326,"right":330,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":326,"left":179,"right":325,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":168,"right":178,"